in rtabmap source, replace following files and make;make install:

guilib/include/rtabmap/gui/ImageView.h
guilib/src/DatabaseViewer.cpp
guilib/src/ImageView.cpp
guilib/src/ui/DatabaseViewer


Run rtabmap-databaseViewer

click on upper-left corner of IMAGE (with no text in label (left side textbox of the 3 )).
This will record (X,Y) to compute relative position.

to record label:
    enter text in label textbox
    click on point on image
    if good value, it will say "Good value recorded", otherwise "NaN detected!"
